<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>postgresql on 대충어쩌고저쩌고샬라샬라</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/tags/postgresql/</link><description>Recent content in postgresql on 대충어쩌고저쩌고샬라샬라</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://dntco43u.github.io/tags/postgresql/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>tag-edit</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/dev/tag-edit/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dntco43u.github.io/dev/tag-edit/</guid><description>&lt;div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert"&gt;&lt;div class="h4 alert-heading" role="heading"&gt;작성 중&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>med-exam</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/dev/med-exam/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dntco43u.github.io/dev/med-exam/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="데모-페이지"&gt;데모 페이지 &lt;sup id="fnref:1"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:1" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%eb%8d%b0%eb%aa%a8-%ed%8e%98%ec%9d%b4%ec%a7%80" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://gr.gvp6nx1a.duckdns.org/d/fdyt7rjk3owzkd/med-exam?orgId=1"&gt;데모 페이지 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://agknwpt3.grafana.net/d/fdyt7rjk3owzkd/med-exam?orgId=1&amp;amp;from=2024-07-23T15:00:00.000Z&amp;amp;to=2024-09-09T14:59:59.000Z&amp;amp;timezone=Asia%2FSeoul&amp;amp;var-usr_id=9VFsW2u8mIqFXMlG7f6irg%3D%3D&amp;amp;var-exam_type_cd=002&amp;amp;var-exam_id=RT51KR-PK01&amp;amp;var-rslt_ymd=$__all&amp;amp;var-exam_a_gb_cd=$__all&amp;amp;var-grdng_cd=$__all&amp;amp;var-exam_b_gb_cd=$__all&amp;amp;var-ai_model=$__all"&gt;데모 페이지 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="dockerfile"&gt;Dockerfile&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#dockerfile" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vi /opt/python/Dockerfile
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-dockerfile" data-lang="dockerfile"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;python:3-slim&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#bf616a"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#bf616a"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;ENV&lt;/span&gt; TZ&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;Asia/Seoul&lt;span style="color:#bf616a"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#bf616a"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1;font-weight:bold"&gt;RUN&lt;/span&gt; apt-get update &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; apt-get install -y python3 &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; python -m pip install --no-cache-dir --upgrade pip &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; pycryptodome &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; psycopg2-binary &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; requests bs4 lxml &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; selenium &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; deep-translator deepl &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; python-telegram-bot &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; g4f&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;all&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; openai groq google-generativeai &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; apt-get autoremove -y &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; apt-get clean autoclean &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*&lt;span style="color:#bf616a"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker build -t e7hnr8ov/python:3-slim /opt/python
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="py_med_examsh"&gt;py_med_exam.sh &lt;sup id="fnref:2"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:2" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#py_med_examsh" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#5e81ac;font-style:italic"&gt;#!/bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#5e81ac;font-style:italic"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# py_med_exam&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;source&lt;/span&gt; /home/dev/.bashrc
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;source&lt;/span&gt; /home/dev/.local/bin/utils.sh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;container&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;py-med-exam&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker ps -q --filter &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;name=&lt;/span&gt;$container&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#eceff4"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; xargs -r docker stop
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sleep &lt;span style="color:#b48ead"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker run &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; -i --rm --name&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$container&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --network&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;dev --user&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;0:0 &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; --add-host&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;host.docker.internal:host-gateway &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; --env-file&lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/opt/python/.env &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; -v /home/dev/workspace/med_exam:/opt/python:rw &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; e7hnr8ov/python:3-slim &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; python /opt/python/med_exam.py &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;$@&lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="troubleshooting"&gt;Troubleshooting&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#troubleshooting" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="alert alert-info" role="alert"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;python 패키지 g4f 프롬프트 1000자 제한. &lt;sup id="fnref:3"&gt;&lt;a href="#fn:3" class="footnote-ref" role="doc-noteref"&gt;3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>postgresql</title><link>https://dntco43u.github.io/infra/postgresql/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dntco43u.github.io/infra/postgresql/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="구성"&gt;구성&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%ea%b5%ac%ec%84%b1" aria-label="Heading self-link"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert"&gt;&lt;div class="h4 alert-heading" role="heading"&gt;사용자 구성&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;데이터베이스 앱은 오버헤드, 자원 경쟁 방지를 위해 docker가 아닌 package로 설치합니다.&lt;br&gt;
sslmode=require, 사설 인증서로 외부 접속 개방하는 구성.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo rm -rf /var/lib/pgsql &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo dnf module remove -y postgresql:16/server &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo dnf module install -y postgresql:16/server &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#ebcb8b"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;sudo postgresql-setup --initdb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo vi /var/lib/pgsql/data/pg_hba.conf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ini" data-lang="ini"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# &amp;#34;local&amp;#34; is for Unix domain socket connections only&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;local all all trust&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# IPv4 local connections:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;host all all 127.0.0.1/32 trust&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# IPv6 local connections:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;host all all ::1/128 trust&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# Allow replication connections from localhost, by a user with the&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# replication privilege.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;local replication all trust&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;host replication all 127.0.0.1/32 trust&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;host replication all ::1/128 trust&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;host all all all scram-sha-256&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo vi /var/lib/pgsql/data/postgresql.conf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d8dee9;background-color:#2e3440;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ini" data-lang="ini"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# - Connection Settings -&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;listen_addresses&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;*&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# - Authentication -&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;password_encryption&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;scram-sha-256&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#616e87;font-style:italic"&gt;# - SSL -&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;ssl&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;on&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;ssl_cert_file&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;/var/lib/pgsql/server.crt&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;ssl_key_file&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39;/var/lib/pgsql/server.key&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#8fbcbb"&gt;ssl_ciphers&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#81a1c1"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a3be8c"&gt;&amp;#39; ECDHE-ECDSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:ECDHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384:ECDHE-ECDSA-CHACHA20-POLY1305:ECDHE-RSA-CHACHA20-POLY1305:ECDHE-ARIA256-GCM-SHA384:DHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
